NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Util::FileGenerator - helper to generate files with little
    repetition in a PluginBundle

VERSION
    version 0.120090

METHODS
  combine_with
        my @plugins_with_generated_files = $gen->combine_with( @plain_plugins );

    Given an array containing specs for a plugin bundle this method returns
    an array with the necessary exclusions, generators and copiers added.

  generators
        my @generator_plugins = $gen->generators;

    Returns an array with the necessary generators for inclusion in a plugin
    bundle.

  file_names
        my @generated_files = $gen->file_names;

    Returns an array with the file names of the generated files.

  copiers
        my @generated_files = $gen->copiers;

    Returns an array with the necessary copiers for inclusion in a plugin
    bundle.

